---
import Mascot from '../Mascot.astro';
---
<section class="slide slide-callback-queue">
  <div class="content">
    <h2 class="title">La Callback Queue <span class="subtitle-inline">(Cola de macrotareas)</span></h2>

    <div class="main-grid">
      <div class="queue-visual" aria-label="Diagrama de cola de callbacks esperando ser procesados">
        <div class="queue-label">Callback Queue</div>

        <div class="queue-container">
          <!-- Entrada -->
          <div class="queue-entry">
            <span class="entry-icon">⬇️</span>
            <span class="entry-text">Desde Web APIs</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Cola de callbacks -->
          <div class="queue-track">
            <div class="queue-item item-1">
              <span class="item-icon">⏱</span>
              <span>setTimeout cb</span>
            </div>
            <div class="queue-item item-2">
              <span class="item-icon">🖱</span>
              <span>click handler</span>
            </div>
            <div class="queue-item item-3">
              <span class="item-icon">🔁</span>
              <span>setInterval cb</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Salida -->
          <div class="queue-exit">
            <span class="exit-text">Al Call Stack</span>
            <span class="exit-icon">➡️</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <svg class="event-loop-arrow" viewBox="0 0 200 40" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
          <text x="100" y="14" text-anchor="middle" fill="#F59E0B" font-size="9" font-weight="bold">
            Solo cuando el Call Stack está vacío
          </text>
          <path d="M20 24 L180 24" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="5,3" marker-end="url(#arrowOrange)"/>
          <defs>
            <marker id="arrowOrange" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto">
              <path d="M0,0 L6,3 L0,6 Z" fill="#F59E0B"/>
            </marker>
          </defs>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="explanation">
        <div class="description-card">
          <p>
            Cuando un ayudante del navegador termina su trabajo, pone el resultado
            en esta cola para que JavaScript lo procese.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="examples-list">
          <h3 class="examples-title">Ejemplos de macrotareas</h3>
          <div class="example-item">
            <code>setTimeout(fn, delay)</code>
            <span>Ejecuta fn después de delay ms</span>
          </div>
          <div class="example-item">
            <code>setInterval(fn, delay)</code>
            <span>Ejecuta fn repetidamente cada delay ms</span>
          </div>
          <div class="example-item">
            <code>addEventListener('click', fn)</code>
            <span>Ejecuta fn cuando el usuario hace click</span>
          </div>
          <div class="example-item">
            <code>MessageChannel</code>
            <span>Comunicación entre contextos</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-card">
          <span class="rule-icon">⚠️</span>
          <p>
            El Event Loop solo mueve un callback de la cola al Call Stack
            <strong>cuando el Call Stack está completamente vacío</strong>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Mascot message="Solo proceso callbacks cuando el Call Stack está vacío. ¡Paciencia!" mood="explaining" />
</section>

<style>
  .slide-callback-queue {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 70%, var(--color-callback-queue-bg) 0%, var(--color-bg) 60%);
  }

  .content {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 860px;
    padding: var(--space-8);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-callback-queue);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .subtitle-inline {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .main-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.3fr;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Queue visual */
  .queue-visual {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .queue-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-callback-queue);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .queue-container {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-callback-queue);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-4);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .queue-entry, .queue-exit {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .queue-exit {
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  .queue-track {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .queue-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    animation: fadeSlide 0.4s ease both;
  }

  .item-1 { background: #451A03; color: #FCD34D; border: 1px solid #F59E0B; animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .item-2 { background: #3d1a00; color: #FCA5A5; border: 1px solid #EF4444; animation-delay: 0.25s; }
  .item-3 { background: #3a1a00; color: #FDE68A; border: 1px solid #D97706; animation-delay: 0.4s; }

  @keyframes fadeSlide {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-8px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
  }

  .item-icon {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
  }

  .event-loop-arrow {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  /* Explanation */
  .explanation {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .description-card {
    background: var(--color-callback-queue-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-callback-queue);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-4);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .examples-title {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .examples-list {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-4);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .example-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
    padding: var(--space-2) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .example-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .example-item code {
    color: var(--color-callback-queue);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  .example-item span {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
  }

  .rule-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    background: #2a1500;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-callback-queue);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-4);
  }

  .rule-icon {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .rule-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .rule-card strong {
    color: var(--color-callback-queue);
  }
</style>
